g.title: j624455684
g.text: I've never been called an "asshat" before.

g.title: j1286594259
g.text: I've got more where that came from.

g.title: j1040715900
g.text: I'm sure I'll hear all your clever insults eventually.

g.title: j1023011013
g.text: I thought I'd experienced most of the world, until I met you.

g.title: j3602812207
g.text: That whole "I have feelings for you" thing? It was a joke.

g.title: j18569919
g.text: I-- wait. Sorry. No. I meant it. Go on.

g.title: j3122350672
g.text: I have a sick sense of humor.

g.title: j2953654090
g.text: When I joined the ICR - even before then, I was a military man.

g.title: j1541998427
g.text: I've lived my entire life with one foot in the grave. I've always been as good as dead.

g.title: j3628216121
g.text: And it's never been more true than now. Look at me. I mean *look at me.*

g.title: j2910355737
g.text: So...we've had a chance to get to know each other. We've grown a bit close, yeah? You...make me laugh.

g.title: j2034999318
g.text: You make me smile more than I have in years.

g.title: j3907525063
g.text: But how can you want to be with someone...like me?

g.title: j76165214
g.text: Arthur, you mean more to me than you can imagine.

g.title: j2118805316
g.text: I have a thing for toaster ovens?

g.title: j1253440253
g.text: I don't care "what's happened to you."

g.title: j498886212
g.text: And you've instantly made me regret this.

g.title: j4052866048
g.text: Let me know if you change your mind.

g.title: j3466497720
g.text: You're *you.* And that's what I'm here for. And that's who I want to be with.

g.title: j2816168189
g.text: Of everything that's happened in this cursed year, I never dreamed...never even imagined...

g.title: j2015103494
g.text: You really want to try this? Us?

g.title: j3198770595
g.text: Maybe not yet? Can we take more time? [End.]
